00:14:16.608 --> 00:14:20.108
coverage for salpingectomy itself when it's being offered as an

232
00:14:20.168 --> 00:14:21.728
alternative to tubal ligation,

233
00:14:22.668 --> 00:14:26.308
or lack of coverage of related services

234
00:14:26.368 --> 00:14:29.448
like anesthesia and pathology.

235
00:14:31.627 --> 00:14:35.308
And then there's health policy. Outdated health policy is

236
00:14:35.368 --> 00:14:38.428
another often related major access barrier.

237
00:14:38.948 --> 00:14:42.908
And many don't realize it, but in states like Maryland, where

238
00:14:43.068 --> 00:14:46.628
I live, salpingectomy is still excluded from Medicaid

239
00:14:46.748 --> 00:14:48.708
