240
00:14:49.588 --> 00:14:53.428
And since private insurers often follow suit, this systematically

241
00:14:53.488 --> 00:14:57.408
limits access to salpingectomy as a practical alternative to

242
00:14:57.488 --> 00:14:58.488
tubal ligation.

243
00:14:59.548 --> 00:15:03.408
Which is really a challenge because there's a growing body

244
00:15:03.468 --> 00:15:07.388
of cost-effectiveness evidence supporting salpingectomy for

