00:15:19.208 --> 00:15:19.908
prevention.

249
00:15:21.548 --> 00:15:24.488
And then there are the massive awareness barriers,

250
00:15:25.308 --> 00:15:27.468
and these are really just profound.

251
00:15:27.928 --> 00:15:31.828
